The VERTICES are extracted of a PLSV i.e.
Point, Line, Surface, Volume. 

Give the TYPE ( P or L or S or V ), then its NAME.

Example:  L;  CONTOUR; 
          deffunc PLANXY(x,y,z); PLANXY = (z=0); endfunc;
          PLANXY;
extract the vertices of the LINE CONTOUR
of which the 3 coordinates x,y,z gives true by PLANXY
(here, all the vertices of the line CONTOUR on the PLANE z=0)
